# Cloud vs. Local AI: Comparative Test Results
**Test Date:** January 24, 2026
**Conducted by:** William Edward Beckham III | CSC-113-0901

---

## Purpose

To validate the local AI infrastructure against commercial cloud alternatives across identical prompts, and to establish a documented baseline for tool selection decisions going forward. This test directly informed the operational rule that governs how the infrastructure is used.

